304
00:18:18,040 --> 00:18:21,399
If you want to buy me something, buy me ice cream.

305
00:18:21,400 --> 00:18:23,199
But you never eat things that are too sweet.

306
00:18:23,200 --> 00:18:24,780
None of your business.

307
