00:18:50,380 --> 00:18:52,520
are reunions after a long time."

311
00:18:52,520 --> 00:18:53,599
Think about it.

312
00:18:53,600 --> 00:18:57,039
We've both been to Mr. Wang's house, both walked this stone road,

313
00:18:57,040 --> 00:18:58,879
both taken photos in the same room.

314
00:18:58,880 --> 00:19:01,879
