321
00:19:26,320 --> 00:19:29,100
I mean... this is the newest flavor.

322
00:19:29,100 --> 00:19:31,580
Do you want to smell it?

323
00:19:31,580 --> 00:19:33,400
Nothing more.

324
00:19:49,560 --> 00:19:51,060
Not bad.

325
00:19:52,080 --> 00:19:54,520
 Was that an indirect kiss? 

326
00:19:54,520 --> 00:19:56,620
 This is so awkward. 

327
00:19:56,620 --> 00:19:58,420
 What should I do? 

328
00:19:58,420 --> 00:20:00,960
 Should I bring up some other topic? 

329
00:20:00,960 --> 00:20:03,060
 What to chat about? 

330
00:20:06,040 --> 00:20:09,160
Boss, you looked pretty handsome in that photo

331
00:20:09,160 --> 00:20:11,040
