332
00:20:12,560 --> 00:20:14,720
Only when I was young?

333
00:20:15,640 --> 00:20:17,940
No. I mean.

334
00:20:17,940 --> 00:20:20,799
When you were young, there must have been a lot of people who liked you.

335
00:20:20,800 --> 00:20:24,420
Someone who fits you must be talented and beautiful.

336
00:20:24,420 --> 00:20:26,600
Born with natural beauty.

337
00:20:27,560 --> 00:20:31,139
 Jiang Xiaoning, what are you saying? 

338
00:20:35,600 --> 00:20:38,700
Chen Wenwen is my ex-girlfriend.

339
00:20:42,240 --> 00:20:44,480
Why are you suddenly talking about this?

340
00:20:44,480 --> 00:20:46,119
I've never asked.

341
00:20:46,120 --> 00:20:49,760
Also, I don't really care about that.

342
00:20:51,160 --> 00:20:52,900
You don't care?

343
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:54,039
Fine.

344
00:20:54,040 --> 00:20:55,120
I won't talk about it then.

345
00:20:56,800 --> 00:21:00,039
But it's fine if you want to talk about it.

346
00:21:00,040 --> 00:21:02,780
It's raining and we can't leave anyway.

347
00:21:06,080 --> 00:21:09,799
Chen Wenwen and I started dating after graduating high school.

348
00:21:09,800 --> 00:21:12,920
After that, I went to study abroad.

349
00:21:12,920 --> 00:21:14,599
We had been managing a long-distance relationship

350
00:21:14,600 --> 00:21:16,039
in two different countries.

351
00:21:16,040 --> 00:21:17,599
During the summer break of my first year in university,

352
00:21:17,600 --> 00:21:19,260
I came back to China.

353
00:21:19,260 --> 00:21:22,900
However, something happened and we broke up.

354
00:21:23,680 --> 00:21:27,320
After that, we've never contacted each other.

355
00:21:28,440 --> 00:21:31,960
