356
00:21:33,360 --> 00:21:35,239
 Yes. It's my fault. 

357
00:21:35,239 --> 00:21:36,839
 It's all my fault. 

358
00:21:36,840 --> 00:21:40,879
 I'm a crow who always brings misfortune. 

359
00:21:42,480 --> 00:21:44,540
But it's fine.

360
00:21:44,540 --> 00:21:47,980
I consider it has come to a full stop.

361
00:21:49,000 --> 00:21:51,300
A full stop?

362
00:21:51,300 --> 00:21:55,239
Isn't it a comma? Or an ellipsis?

363
00:21:59,000 --> 00:22:01,999
I mean who would be willing to have a full stop

364
00:22:02,000 --> 00:22:04,960
