367
00:22:14,280 --> 00:22:17,540
I won't decline this honor.

368
00:22:25,400 --> 00:22:28,339
Boss, there's a cat.

369
00:22:28,339 --> 00:22:31,099
Hold this for me. Come on.

370
00:22:35,740 --> 00:22:38,160
It's so cute.

371
00:22:38,880 --> 00:22:41,080
Baby.

372
00:22:41,080 --> 00:22:45,020
Boss, it's so cute.

373
00:22:45,020 --> 00:22:47,220
Do you want to pet it?

374
00:22:47,220 --> 00:22:48,319
No.

375
00:22:48,319 --> 00:22:50,659
I don't like animals that shed.

376
00:22:50,659 --> 00:22:53,319
Trust me, pet it. You'll fall in love with it.

377
00:22:53,319 --> 00:22:55,739
Just pet it once. Come on.

378
00:23:00,200 --> 00:23:03,659
How do you feel? Isn't its hair so silky?

379
00:23:07,700 --> 00:23:10,600
What does it mean when it looks at me in this way?

380
00:23:10,600 --> 00:23:12,139
It likes you.

381
00:23:12,139 --> 00:23:15,660
It knows that following the right owner will allow it to eat well.

382
00:23:20,000 --> 00:23:21,940
It doesn't have an owner.

383
00:23:21,940 --> 00:23:25,940
It looks like it's a stray cat.

384
00:23:27,920 --> 00:23:31,499
Boss, why don't we take it back and adopt it?

385
00:23:32,900 --> 00:23:34,099
Adopt it?

386
00:23:34,099 --> 00:23:36,039
Boss, look at you.

387
00:23:36,039 --> 00:23:39,359
You're handsome, talented, and kind.

388
00:23:39,360 --> 00:23:41,399
Moreover, your apartment is spacious.

389
00:23:41,400 --> 00:23:44,419
If I bring it back, I won't have time to take care of it

390
00:23:44,419 --> 00:23:46,440
since my grandma and auntie are not in good health.

391
00:23:46,440 --> 00:23:48,240
Boss.

392
00:23:51,300 --> 00:23:54,079
- Well, let me think about it. 
 - Okay.

393
00:23:54,079 --> 00:23:56,540
If you're thinking about it, I need to make it clear.

394
00:23:56,540 --> 00:23:58,820
If you adopt it, you can't abandon it.

395
00:23:58,820 --> 00:24:02,479
You should feed it good food, bathe it, be responsible for it.

396
00:24:02,479 --> 00:24:04,359
Otherwise, you shouldn't adopt it.

397
00:24:04,359 --> 00:24:06,540
If it knows how good it feels to be taken care of by an owner,

398
00:24:06,540 --> 00:24:09,280
it won't be able to revert back to its current lifestyle.

399
00:24:12,500 --> 00:24:16,079
Temporarily. It can stay at my place temporarily.

400
00:24:16,079 --> 00:24:18,839
Then can I go visit it frequently at your place?

401
00:24:18,840 --> 00:24:21,040
Of course, you need to come and visit. Otherwise, am I supposed to raise it by myself?

402
00:24:21,040 --> 00:24:23,599
Great. Thank you, Boss.

403
00:24:25,420 --> 00:24:28,340
Should we give it a name?

404
00:24:28,340 --> 00:24:31,879
Look, your last name is Gu and my last name is Jiang.

405
00:24:31,879 --> 00:24:33,199
Gu Gu?

406
00:24:33,199 --> 00:24:34,519
Jiang Jiang?

407
00:24:34,519 --> 00:24:37,259
- These names don't work. 
 - We can call it Ice Cream.

408
00:24:37,259 --> 00:24:39,419
We ran into it while we were having ice cream.

409
00:24:39,419 --> 00:24:41,840
Why don't we call it Ice Cream?

410
00:24:45,120 --> 00:24:46,620
Okay.

411
00:24:46,620 --> 00:24:49,960
From now on, your name will be Ice Cream.

412
00:24:49,960 --> 00:24:52,760
Ice Cream, Ice Cream.

413
00:24:52,760 --> 00:24:57,140
Boss, give it some ice cream. See if it'll have any.

414
00:24:57,140 --> 00:24:59,599
Feed it. Come on.

415
00:25:01,800 --> 00:25:04,219
- Come on. 
 - Do you want to have any?

416
00:25:06,680 --> 00:25:08,280
How about this one?

417
00:25:09,280 --> 00:25:11,500
You can choose.

418
00:25:21,960 --> 00:25:24,019
You should behave, understand?

419
00:25:24,019 --> 00:25:26,299
Adapting to the environment is basic.

420
00:25:26,299 --> 00:25:28,659
Don't think I can't hold you accountable even though you look cute.

421
00:25:28,659 --> 00:25:32,060
If you want to stay at my place, you must have a bath.

422
00:25:32,060 --> 00:25:33,680
Come here.

423
00:25:35,200 --> 00:25:37,200
I asked you to come here.

424
00:25:37,860 --> 00:25:39,279
You're smart.

425
00:25:39,279 --> 00:25:40,939
You know this is the bathroom.

426
00:25:40,939 --> 00:25:42,419
Come, come, come.

427
00:25:42,419 --> 00:25:46,220
From now on, here is where you take baths.

428
00:26:25,120 --> 00:26:27,239
 Ice Cream is so cute. 

429
00:26:27,239 --> 00:26:29,099
 I feel happy when I see you. 

430
00:26:29,099 --> 00:26:30,699
 But what makes me happier 

431
00:26:30,699 --> 00:26:34,359
 is being able to visit you at Boss' place often. 

