00:27:25,220 --> 00:27:29,000
 Miss Crow and Mr. Lizard. 

434
00:27:37,440 --> 00:27:39,040
Boss.

435
00:27:44,240 --> 00:27:46,379
Suddenly behaving so well.

436
00:27:46,379 --> 00:27:48,419
I hope you won't lose your passion too fast.

437
00:27:48,419 --> 00:27:51,039
Thank you, Boss. I'll try to keep it up.

438
00:27:51,039 --> 00:27:54,819
If there's nothing else, I'll go back to keep reading Mr. Wang's notes.

439
00:27:54,819 --> 00:27:58,119
Okay. When you're done with it, let me take a look at it, too.

440
00:27:58,119 --> 00:28:00,999
Boss, I really do want to let you have a look at it.

441
00:28:00,999 --> 00:28:04,079
However, this is Mr. Wang's private belongings.

442
00:28:04,079 --> 00:28:07,160
It's not good to pass it around.

443
00:28:07,160 --> 00:28:09,619
I noticed that after we came back from the business trip,

444
00:28:09,619 --> 00:28:11,520
you've become more and more bold.

445
00:28:11,520 --> 00:28:14,880
Director Gu... Xiaoning is here, too.

446
00:28:14,880 --> 00:28:16,780
I was just looking for you.

447
00:28:17,700 --> 00:28:19,579
