449
00:28:21,799 --> 00:28:26,140
I'm afraid I won't have time for Chen Wenwen's exhibition.

450
00:28:27,540 --> 00:28:29,639
Why don't you let Cheng Dong take charge of it?

451
00:28:29,639 --> 00:28:32,620
