466
00:29:52,620 --> 00:29:57,040
I think something big is about to happen in the martial arts world.

467
00:29:57,040 --> 00:30:01,000
A reign of terror is inevitable.

468
00:30:06,220 --> 00:30:10,040
No matter what happens, no matter how many years have passed,

469
00:30:10,040 --> 00:30:11,900
