470
00:30:11,900 --> 00:30:14,380
I only follow my own path.

471
00:30:14,380 --> 00:30:17,620
This hero, would you mind me asking you what path?

472
00:30:18,320 --> 00:30:21,180
The path in your heart.

473
00:30:21,180 --> 00:30:23,019
You can't walk the path in my heart.

474
00:30:23,019 --> 00:30:25,179
To you, there will always be road traffic control.

475
00:30:25,179 --> 00:30:26,899
Why?

476
00:30:26,899 --> 00:30:29,819
Look, you're Empress Dowager.

477
00:30:29,819 --> 00:30:31,659
I'm Commander Ju.

478
00:30:31,659 --> 00:30:34,179
Even our snacks look like a couple.

479
00:30:34,179 --> 00:30:35,839
We were born for each other.

480
00:30:35,839 --> 00:30:38,840
We'll talk once you've become extremely rich.

481
00:30:38,840 --> 00:30:40,300
Can you not act like this?

482
00:30:40,300 --> 00:30:41,480
- What did I do? 
 - Why are you discouraging me?

483
00:30:41,480 --> 00:30:42,979
Is Gu Chuan in his office?

484
00:30:42,979 --> 00:30:45,460
Yes, yes, yes.

485
00:30:50,840 --> 00:30:52,800
Jia Jia, Jia Jia, Jia Jia.

486
00:30:52,800 --> 00:30:54,419
Jia Jia, don't think about it.

487
00:30:54,419 --> 00:30:56,319
