489
00:30:57,680 --> 00:31:00,460
Nothing is impossible.

490
00:31:01,220 --> 00:31:03,920
Why leave me hanging?

491
00:31:04,660 --> 00:31:08,240
My Chuan.

492
00:31:10,900 --> 00:31:12,179
Who bought this for you?

493
00:31:12,179 --> 00:31:13,819
