495
00:31:20,840 --> 00:31:24,640
When did I start liking vanilla?

496
00:31:24,640 --> 00:31:26,600
You don't?

497
00:31:26,600 --> 00:31:27,660
It's not important.

498
00:31:27,660 --> 00:31:31,859
These are fresh from the oven, way more delicious than this, which clearly looks stale.

499
00:31:32,420 --> 00:31:34,500
