511
00:32:13,440 --> 00:32:15,000
Meng Jia.

512
00:32:16,220 --> 00:32:18,659
Director Xu, why are you here?

513
00:32:18,659 --> 00:32:21,400
I thought I just saw a ghost.

514
00:32:21,400 --> 00:32:23,500
Well.

515
00:32:26,340 --> 00:32:27,339
Be my girlfriend.

516
00:32:27,339 --> 00:32:29,640
Be your girlfriend?

517
00:32:34,480 --> 00:32:36,080
Come with me.

518
00:32:36,080 --> 00:32:38,639
Get on with your work. Do your work. Nothing is happening here.

519
00:32:43,120 --> 00:32:44,579
- Today... 
 - Brother Kai.

520
00:32:44,579 --> 00:32:45,919
Brother Kai, what's the matter?

521
00:32:45,919 --> 00:32:47,919
Brother Kai. Mr... Mr. Cheng.

522
00:32:47,919 --> 00:32:50,439
- Brother Kai. 
 - Brother Kai.

523
00:32:58,940 --> 00:33:02,720
